{"tid":1537292,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"嶺南學生小心","createTime":"2019-09-04T01:15:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-05T08:33:40.000Z","uid":89937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b99f2b3eb9f4e34e2666720bbdfa8f4cb00b32ef","tid":1537292,"uid":89937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T01:15:05.000Z","msg":"收到風，嶺南學生喺宿舍房門貼政治文宣既話，保安部叫保安影低，會交畀學校"},{"pid":"8b550c781c011cb9449ae9ea0834c193aeffd083","tid":1537292,"uid":52727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T01:15:30.000Z","msg":"【教學】將Facebook/Youtube 影片文宣轉換成Twitter 文宣<br />\r\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1537277\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1537277</a><br />\r\n<br />\r\n1. 註冊Twitter 帳號。<br />\r\n2. 找到要post 上Twitter 的影片。<br />\r\n3. 複制facebook影片連結貼上到以下網頁 (需要登入及縛定Twitter 帳戶， facebook影片分享必需是公開)。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<a href=\"https://transferring-videos.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftransferring-videos.com&d=8FXSm2SwW1drj%2BZzPONh3LJtyMJyNHaGyUrVEdcKl1A%3D&h=45024351\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://transferring-videos.com</a><br />\r\n<br />\r\n4. 等待轉換時輸入英文標題，及加上 #chinazi 等 hash tag。<br />\r\n5. 選擇發佈至 Twitter。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n6. 【重要】我諗大家嘅Twitter應該都冇乜人follow, 記得copy自己Twitter post 嘅link, 然後貼上到名人的Twitter post 上！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\r\n<br />\r\n我做咗幾日已經多咗好多外國人睇，甚至開始有支那打手過黎留言。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9cb292dcb0f062880e9eb7bf550dbd41e3a8cff","tid":1537292,"uid":92448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T01:15:48.000Z","msg":"全校下一齊做會點？"},{"pid":"4a6c126b0a80b7b0a100a5c7aec9952f7428b870","tid":1537292,"uid":271434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T08:33:40.000Z","msg":"好多保安管理公司主管都請咗退休或離職警察！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1504217\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1504217</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}